---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/CTASection';
import ServiceForm from '../../components/ServiceForm';
import Reviews from '../../components/Reviews';
import LicenseBadges from '../../components/LicenseBadges.astro';
import BrandsSection from '../../components/BrandsSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Furnace Installation Laguna Hills CA | HiLo Heating and Air" description="Professional furnace installation in Laguna Hills, CA. Expert setup with proper sizing and quality workmanship from HiLo Heating and Air.">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-blue-800 py-20 sm:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Furnace Installation Laguna Hills CA</h1>
        <p class="text-white/80 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Winters here don't get brutal, but they get cold enough — and an old, struggling furnace makes itself known fast on those chilly nights. HiLo Heating and Air handles furnace installation homeowners trust.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <LicenseBadges />

    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg">
        <p>Winters here don't get brutal, but they get cold enough — and an old, struggling furnace makes itself known fast on those chilly nights. If yours is wheezing through its last season, or you're building out a new space that needs heat from scratch, Hilo Heating and Air handles <strong>furnace installation Laguna Hills CA</strong> homeowners trust to get it done right the first time.</p>

        <h2>When It's Time to Replace, Not Repair</h2>
        <p>There's a point where fixing an old furnace stops making sense. If yours is pushing fifteen-plus years, needs repairs every other winter, or your energy bills keep climbing despite nothing changing — that's usually the signal. We'll always tell you honestly if a repair will hold, but when it won't, <strong>furnace installation Laguna Hills CA</strong> residents call us for is the more practical move long-term. New systems run quieter, use less energy, and don't leave you stranded on the coldest night of the year wondering if this is the time it finally dies for good.</p>

        <h2>Picking the Right System for Your Home</h2>
        <p>Not every furnace fits every house. Square footage, ductwork condition, insulation, even how your home is laid out — all of it affects what size and type actually makes sense. We walk through that with you before recommending anything. Most <strong>furnace installation Laguna Hills CA</strong> projects start with a proper load calculation, not just swapping in whatever's closest in size to the old unit. Get that step wrong and you end up with a furnace that's either working too hard or short-cycling constantly — neither is good for the equipment or your wallet.</p>

        <h2>What Installation Day Looks Like</h2>
        <p>We're not interested in cutting corners just to finish faster. A typical <strong>furnace installation Laguna Hills CA</strong> job involves removing the old unit, checking ductwork for leaks or damage, setting the new system, and testing it thoroughly before we consider the job done. Most installs wrap up in a single day. We walk you through the new thermostat, explain basic maintenance, and make sure everything's running the way it should before we leave — not just turned on and hoped for the best.</p>

        <h2>Local Installers Who Know the Area</h2>
        <p>Being based nearby means we already understand how Laguna Hills homes are built, what permitting typically involves, and which furnace sizes tend to work best for the area's housing styles. Every <strong>furnace installation Laguna Hills CA</strong> job is done to code, backed by a warranty on both labor and equipment, and handled by a team that's still around if anything needs adjusting once winter actually arrives.</p>
        <p>If your furnace is on its last legs, or you're starting from zero, give Hilo Heating and Air a call. We'd rather help you choose the right system upfront than have you calling back in two years.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
          <div>
            <span class="inline-block bg-brand-blue/10 text-brand-blue text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4">Schedule Service</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-4">Get a Free Estimate</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Fill out the form and our team will get back to you within 15 minutes. Same-day service available.</p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Same-Day Service Available</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Free Diagnostics with Repair</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0115.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 013 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 003 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Upfront Pricing, No Hidden Fees</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ServiceForm client:load />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <Reviews client:visible />
    <BrandsSection />

    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-slate-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">How do I know if I need a new furnace or just a repair?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Age, repair frequency, and rising energy bills are the main signs. We'll give you an honest read before recommending replacement.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">How long does a typical installation take?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Most jobs wrap up in a single day, sometimes longer if ductwork needs work too.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Will you help me pick the right size furnace?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yes, we run a proper load calculation based on your home's size and layout rather than just matching the old unit.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Is the new furnace covered under warranty?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yes, both labor and equipment are covered.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Do I need a permit for furnace installation?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Usually, yes — we handle that process for you as part of the job.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">What brands do you install?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">We work with most major furnace brands and can recommend options based on your budget and home.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Are your installers licensed?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Every technician is fully licensed and insured.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">What if something feels off after installation?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Just call us — we'll come back out and make it right under warranty.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-brand-blue/5 py-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-brand-blue font-semibold">HiLo Heating and Air · 8131 Electric Ave, Stanton, CA 90680, United States</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-1"><a href="tel:+17148535534" class="hover:text-brand-red transition">(714) 853-5534</a> · <a href="mailto:info@hiloheatingandair.com" class="hover:text-brand-red transition">info@hiloheatingandair.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <CTASection client:visible />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
